  (2) Edit Mode
    Keysym      (Command)| Function
    ---------------------+-------------------------------------------------
    PF1                  | Switch between Hiragana and Katakana
    PF2                  | Switch between full width and half width
    PF3                  | Switch between Romaji and direct input
    PF4                  | Switch to dictionary manipulation
    Kanji            ^W  | Display all candidates (large phrase)
                     ^Z  | Display all candidates (small phrase)
    Execute          ^L  | Confirm a conversion
    Right            ^F  | Move the phrase indication to the right
    Left             ^B  | Move the phrase indication to the left
    Down             ^N  | Display the next candidate (group)
    Up               ^P  | Display the previous candidate (group)
    Meta + Right     ^E  | Move the phrase indication to the right end
		         | of the line
    Meta + Left      ^A  | Move the phrase indication to the left end
		         | of the line
    Meta + Up        ^K  | Do not convert
    F14              ^O  | Increase the size of the phrase by one character
    F13              ^I  | Decrease the size of the phrase by one character
    Meta + F11       ^T  | Registration function
                     ^C  | Confirm and switch to input mode
                ^SP  ^@  | Turn on/off the connection to uum
    ---------------------+-------------------------------------------------

  (3) Dictionary Mode
    Keysym      (Command)| Function
    ---------------------+-------------------------------------------------
    PF1                  | Switch between hiragana and katakana
    PF2                  | Switch between full and half width
    PF3                  | Switch between Romaji and direct input
    Right            ^F  | Move the cursor or the reverse video portion
	                 | to the right
    Left             ^B  | Move the cursor or the reverse video portion
		         | to the left
    Down             ^N  | Display the next selection item group
    Up               ^P  | Display the previous selection item group
    F11              ^D  | Delete
    Meta + Right     ^E  | Move the cursor or the reverse video portion
		         | to the right end of the line
    Meta + Left      ^A  | Move the cursor or the reverse video portion
		         | to the left end of the line
    Meta + Down      ^G  | Quit dictionary mode
    F12              ^U  | Use/Don't use
                ^SP  ^@  | Turn on/off the connection to uum
    ---------------------+-------------------------------------------------

